    {
      "id": "ttv-pattern-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Pattern Notes",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 260,
        "y": 320
      },
      "width": 620,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Pattern Notes\n\nUse `Title` for framing, `Type Definition` for declared identity, `UI View` as the default `Port` surface for host-facing destinations, `Node View` for the primary on-graph surface, and `Icon View` for semantic zoom.\n\nAdd extra nodes like `Field` only when the graph needs more declared identity or quick metadata, not as part of the minimum graph-root pattern."
      }
    },
    {
